[DQR.IFRS.0105.9556] The following elements are in the presentation linkbase of 02 - Profit or loss but are not included in any calculation relationship in the filing. gestampautomocion:EarningPerShareDiluted, gestampautomocion:EarningsPerShareBasic All elements appearing in the face of the financial statements should be included in a calculation relationship somewhere in the filing.
This rule will produce an error irrespective of a fact value being entered for the item(s) listed above.
Rule Element Id:9556 Rule version: 18.0.0RC1 -

[DQR.IFRS.0129.9625] It is expected that ProfitLossAttributableToOwnersOfParent with a value of -151,055,000 reported in the network role http://gestampautomocion.com/xbrl/2021/roles/ProfitOrLoss should be equal to the dimensionally qualified concept, ProfitLoss with the dimension ifrs-full:ComponentsOfEquityAxis = ifrs-full:EquityAttributableToOwnersOfParentMember and a reported value of 151,055,000 multiplied by 1. This value appears in the network role http://gestampautomocion.com/xbrl/2021/roles/StatementOfChangesInEquity. This error occurs when the dimensionally qualified fact is not equal to the value input for the non dimensional item.
The properties of this ifrs-full:ProfitLossAttributableToOwnersOfParent fact are:
Period : 2020-01-01 to 2020-12-31 Dimensions : Unit : EUR Decimals of ProfitLossAttributableToOwnersOfParent : -3 Decimals of ProfitLoss : -3 Rule version: 18.0.0RC1 - https://filings.xbrl.org/95980020140005484363/2021-12-31/ESEF/ES/0/95980020140005484363-2021-12-31-en.zip/95980020140005484363-2021-12-31-en/reports/95980020140005484363-2021-12-31-en.xhtml 21372
